content.rendered: Peter Andreasen, Marketing Director, Mohamed Youssef Zitouni, Head of IDS, MENA and Amal Vijayan, Key Account Manager, MENA from Danfoss visited the TTE HQ recently. They were greeted by Dilip Sharma, Executive Vice President, Kanchan Koppikar, Marketing & Communications Manager and Shameer Palathingal, Senior Sales Executive, Products & Solutions. Apart from a tour of our headquarters, plans for collaborative future events were made, aimed at strengthening our position as Danfoss’s preferred decarbonization partner, with a focus on long-term value creation for customers.
